Target: OntoBPR is an ontology developed for expressing a back pressure regulator.

Comment: The device that is used to control the back pressure of a reactor.
The task to control the reactor pressure based on its setting. Reactor pressure control is modelled as a saref:Task that can be accomplished by BackPressureRegulator.
The function to adjust the reactor pressure.
The command to adjust the reactor pressure.
The relation between BackPressureRegulator and the reactor pressure control task it can conduct.
The relation identifies that the BackPressureRegulator that can accomplish the reactor pressure control task.
The relation identifies the function of BackPressureRegulator.
The relation between PressureAdjustment function and PressureAdjustmentCommand command.
The relation between PressureAdjustmentCommand command and PressureAdjustment function it can achieve.
